parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Tire failure can lead to loss of control, accidents, and damage to the vehicle, resulting in potential harm to occupants and other road users.
symptoms: Sudden loud noise or explosion
loss of tire pressure
tire tread separation
tire blowout
rubber debris on the road
and potential damage to the vehicle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the spring hanger can cause the suspension to collapse, leading to uneven vehicle leveling, loss of control, and increased risk of accidents.
symptoms: The vehicle is leveled lower than usual
the spring hanger breaks or collapses
the leaf spring is loose or detached from the frame
the frame is sitting loosely on the spring.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden failure of the Goodyear Marathon tire can cause loss of control, accidents, and damage to the vehicle or trailer, potentially leading to injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Tire blowout
tire failure
loss of air pressure
damage to surrounding components such as skirting or axles.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the frame can cause loss of control, accidents, or rollovers, which can lead to serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Cracking or breaking of the frame
particularly at the rear spring shackle
resulting in loss of structural integrity and potential collapse of the vehicle.
